I love the short blonde support-role doctor, but I hate that dark-haired one bc the dark haired one was so  stupid that he was horribly unbelievable as a doctor. How many times did he call the highly known pathologist a "broad"?  Who does that in the professional world?  No one.  He would have been thrown out of every training facility in the United States.  Why couldn't that respectful lovable and good-looking actor stay in that role???  Did you want a minority so badly that they had to scrape the bottom of the barrel for the stupidest one available?
